Package model.web

Class WebMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.web.WebMap
  • public class WebMap
extends java.lang.Object
    int[][] type of a web which additionally includes knowledge to act as a web to be searched . These values are tileStart, tileTarget, value of 0 is considered to be a wall. and name can be used as a file name. Negative values are allowed. Data model to be searched by a AnalysableAlgorithm.

      • isValid

        public boolean isValid()
        Returns:
        true if such a map is considered valid else prints out all errors and returns false, requirements: width and height of map above 0 starting location tileStart exists within map target location tileTarget exists within map target or start point is not a wall LegalFileName.isValidFileName(name) returns true width is less or equal to 10000, height is less or equal to 10000
